## Example

```toon
name: TOON Parser
version: 2.0
unicode: Hello ä¸–ç•Œ ðŸŽ‰

arrays:
  inline[3]: a,b,c
  empty[0]:
  
table[2]{id,name}:
  1,Alice
  2,Bob

users[2]:
  - name: Alice
    score: 100
  - name: Bob
    score: 200

nested:
  data[2]: x,y
```

